			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hey everyone, I know developers have been waiting for SGN GameBar stats, and I&#8217;m happy to report that they just went live! Check it out:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/thephotoherald/2333305593/" title="SGN_Developer_stats by montoya.christian, on Flickr"><img src="http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2057/2333305593_97b9252206_o.png" width="202" height="459" alt="SGN_Developer_stats" /></a></p>
<p>To view the stats for your game, just log in to the <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/sgndeveloper/">SGN Developer application</a> and go the tab &#8220;GameBar Stats.&#8221; Currently, we just have simple cumulative numbers, but soon we will have more in-depth statistics for the past 24 hours as well as graphs to make it all visually appealing. Due time, due time.</p>
<p>Also, I&#8217;m happy to say we have over 40 games in the SGN Platform, and we are working on many more features, both for the GameBar and the Gaming Hub application. Just watch this space, and if you haven&#8217;t joined the SGN Platform yet, then what are you waiting for???</p>
