		<description><![CDATA[As you may have already heard, our Gaming Hub launched this morning with a handful of games from our own library (Warbook, Fight Club, Street Race, Herd a Word, and World Conquest) and since that launch, we have also had another game to join: The Dot Game. This game is a perfect example of the [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>As you may have already heard, our Gaming Hub launched this morning with a handful of games from our own library (Warbook, Fight Club, Street Race, Herd a Word, and World Conquest) and since that launch, we have also had another game to join: <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/thedotgame/">The Dot Game</a>. This game is a perfect example of the kind of high-quality &amp; fun games that we would like to present to the huge community of gamers on Facebook.</p>
<p>We also launched a new version of <a href="http://socialgn.com/">our site</a> today, with our full library of games showcased. I think it&#8217;s really cool.</p>
<p>If you are a game developer and you are looking for more ways to promote your game and increase user loyalty, now is the time to get into our platform! I&#8217;ll be available all day tomorrow to talk so just hit up developers [at] socialgn.com.</p>
