		<description><![CDATA[Hello, game developers! We have been hard at work to bring you the SGN Developer Platform, an extension to the existing social platforms designed to enrich the social gaming realm and make your lives as game developers much easier. You can find the current fruits of our labor at developers.socialgn.com, where I have taken the [...]]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hello, game developers! We have been hard at work to bring you the SGN Developer Platform, an extension to the existing social platforms designed to enrich the social gaming realm and make your lives as game developers much easier. You can find the current fruits of our labor at <a href="http://developers.socialgn.com">developers.socialgn.com</a>, where I have taken the time to explain our Gaming Hub application, our API client libraries, and the criteria for games to join our network. We believe that we have a lot to offer as the largest social gaming network in the world, and we know that by helping to promote great games made by you, we will be making the social gaming community better for everyone. So, let&#8217;s talk. You can feel free to e-mail us at developers [at] socialgn.com, and throughout the day you can always hit us up at GTalk using the same address.</p>
<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/sgndeveloper/~4/358818740" height="1" width="1"/>]]></content:encoded>
